{"tid":531563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到台灣測試手提電話災難警報","createTime":"2018-01-17T03:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T03:20:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c232670f3287a63f3c212c06c478e454d466603d","tid":531563,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180117/large/1516156405_14f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180117%2Flarge%2F1516156405_14f4.jpg&h=44cf1df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國夏威夷與日本，分別都誤發導彈來襲的警告訊息，甚外引來恐慌。今日下午全台的手機用戶都會收到警告訊息，但當局表示這是全台進行的4G災防告警廣播訊息測試，真的是測試，呼籲收到警告後民眾不需要過度緊張。<br />\n<br />\n這是今年第一次進行測試，不同的電訊商會在不同時間進行，例如台灣大哥大在中午12時，遠傳和亞太電信則在下午4時，警告訊息會特別註明「每月災防告警訊息發送測試」。<br />\n<br />\n當局指出，類似的測試今年會每月進行，以確保系統通知健全，但每個月會針對不同區域、不同時間進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180117/57717606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F57717606&d=L34AUgwE3moM9iudM2%2FtZhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0f439cc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F57717606&h=7fd3d6fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180117/57717606</a>"}]}